CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 1, 1956, pg. A11 reads: "Winner - The proud winner of the "Miss WILY" contest, Mildred Ann Briscoe, poses prettily for the camera upon being crowned at Warner's Cinerama Theatre, 336 Fifth Ave. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Full length portrait of "Miss WILY" Mildred Ann Briscoe wearing tiara, light colored evening gown with tulle skirt, and mink stole, posed on stairs of stage in Warner's Cinerama Theatre
